{"tid":1447037,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"討論破解內鬼方法，臥底呢條橋班狗用唔到幾多次。","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:58:29.000Z","uid":42691,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"abe75a7ccb08fc1ddeb855ad22dbeb6e0745e55f","tid":1447037,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"1.共同特徵<br />\n今次係螢光棒，耳機，手錶，紫色濾罐。<br />\n每次都會唔同，但<br />\n大原則係：<br />\n遠處都分到，否則槍手容易打中自己人。<br />\n<br />\n2.(未經證實)唔可以否認自己係警察<br />\n見到身形有別於一般示威者，可以去問下係咪警察。<br />\n當年反新東既示威，警察混入示威者入面，有人問係咪警察，結果啞曬。<br />\n警察執行職務既時候，要承認自己係警務人員，佢地通常都唔答，唔答就係鬼。<br />\n*可以講大話，但面對鏡頭應該唔敢<br />\n*記者可以主動問下<br />\n<br />\n3.張望目標有別於示威者<br />\n佢地唔擔心撤退問題，關心既唔係對面既警察。<br />\n可以參考傻強對白。<br />\n<br />\n4.不時離離合合。<br />\n<br />\n5.落場經驗唔多，唔係好知自己要做咩。<br />\n<br />\n6.一定派飛虎身形，派CID死梗。<br />\n<br />\n未諗到<br />\n諗到再補充<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n經過警察學院訓練，佢地係部隊，行為舉止有相似性，有別於我地呢d散兵游勇。只要細心觀察下具備以上特徵既人，其實一眼就睇得出。<br />\n<br />\n今次係輸零戒備。<br />\n<br />\n今場係輸無戒備之心 <br />\n既然已經浮上水面 <br />\n從今以後<br />\n全力捉鬼下佢地都好難再隱身<br />\n佢地應該唔會短時間內再派內鬼<br />\n就算派咗 都未必敢落單<br />\n佢地都係人 都會驚自己有咩差池<br />\n<br />\n呢條橋最大功用就係瓦解前線互信<br />\n達到不攻自破<br />\n黎緊幾場係會草木皆兵 疑神疑鬼<br />\n但唔緊要<br />\n只要黎緊一兩場捉到鬼<br />\n勇武信心就會返黎"},{"pid":"89ad3fc328cb16d206ab9752362b3fad4b54fb7e","tid":1447037,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:00:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf302b0fbf22d243c67dc23a04db4875ae3616bd","tid":1447037,"uid":143987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"612<br />\n721<br />\n805<br />\n812"},{"pid":"b8092a72e6bcc42a7e02eb9ca281d2505953057a","tid":1447037,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"00ec8f0408a1d974376ede9bd920d333c3a6a959","tid":1447037,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"612,721,812"},{"pid":"c60228315a4e5ffdb19ce91e28fcccd310de38b7","tid":1447037,"uid":280934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n要重整隊型😖😖"},{"pid":"102aea28ee5033050835520d2ff3042f75bb981d","tid":1447037,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:10:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c12e55ab0514d07aedff7b265d407b721b21bceb","tid":1447037,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:21:28.000Z","msg":"教你如何用簡單問題揪出假扮示威者的黑警臥底！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449924</a>"},{"pid":"8666d68fa144b86cbb022a0408362d29370eecfa","tid":1447037,"uid":275475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"教你如何用簡單問題揪出假扮示威者的黑警臥底！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449924</a><br />\n<br />\n用三個簡單問題質問 即刻發現假扮示威者GE黑警臥底！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n精彩片段重溫 早在五年前2014新界東北集會<br />\n黑警已經帶頭製造混亂 然後逃去OR偷拍<br />\n例如叫吳亮星 仆街！大家衝入去！<br />\n被揭發失敗就會用孖葉鎖示威者<br />\n當時李家超不得不承認話有混入人群<br />\n但死撐話無煽動暴力 挑釁群眾<br />\n宜家2019可以證實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警一直假扮示威者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TUfxzVFk8UU&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTUfxzVFk8UU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=4a98fc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TUfxzVFk8UU&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GTPMPmeaF6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGTPMPmeaF6c&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=904b0854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GTPMPmeaF6c</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JYAC-FbNWFI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJYAC-FbNWFI&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=21636fee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JYAC-FbNWFI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eR2TzRJJU_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeR2TzRJJU_k&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=2868a101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eR2TzRJJU_k</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlfphuwNrAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJlfphuwNrAc&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=a4ca38f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlfphuwNrAc</a>"},{"pid":"0eaf836a1e449f76598e572fb59a3149e2fee1a6","tid":1447037,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47b13eb5144cd8d521156060d3143938dcd935cc","tid":1447037,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf1e279ccfbbac9d58cd3c3a86dcfb9d5c956c44","tid":1447037,"uid":133546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba7a0ff9504106c86dccf5a27fc7b17ad416db27","tid":1447037,"uid":268860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e57bcb98b8f8af3b24469fc9ae7e1329a4b6b025","tid":1447037,"uid":42691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:02:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果我係指揮官<br />\n我唔會再派飛虎做臥底<br />\n因為太顯眼<br />\n全部體型一致<br />\n一曝光就要換<br />\n<br />\n黎緊我會選擇派CID<br />\n雖然體型冇咁一致<br />\n但上述既特徵都會有 <br />\n而且缺乏行動力 落場經驗<br />\n更容易被問到口啞啞<br />\n<br />\n如果我係CID上頭要我做臥底<br />\n簡直係送自己去死</span>"},{"pid":"52831bae1b842cd6e7287f6bd689beacd4eb1b5c","tid":1447037,"uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:04:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記者係身邊既時候<br />\n不妨問下可疑人士</span>"},{"pid":"6a18097ab594588d93c803e712a96b2af5efa96f","tid":1447037,"uid":191968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4686a65cca55b3271bf567ac05fbf05761c6aa66","tid":1447037,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f16e7b9b0373b3e7391d8e5243f5348cb4b5076d","tid":1447037,"uid":59363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"暫時應該只會派大隻佬<br />\n一來真係好危險<br />\n二來佢都要確保單人匹馬制服到示威者<br />\n<br />\n建議現場真係要分組互相照顧<br />\n起碼5至6人一組<br />\n就算有一隻係狗，其他人都可以幫手救人"}]}